[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說九色鹿經一卷",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吳月氏優婆塞支謙譯",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昔者，菩薩身為九色鹿；其毛九種色，其角白",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如雪，常在恒水邊飲食水草，常與一烏為知識。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，水中有一溺人隨流來下，或出或沒，得著樹木，仰頭呼天：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「山神、樹神、諸天龍神，何不愍傷於我？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿聞人聲，走到水中，語溺人言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c04_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝莫恐怖！",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝可騎我背上，捉我兩角，我當相負出水。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」既得着岸，鹿大疲極，溺人下地，遶鹿三匝，向鹿叩頭：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「乞與大家作奴供給，使令採取水草。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不用汝也，且各自去，欲報恩者，莫道我在此，人貪我皮角，必來殺我。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，溺人受教而去。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，國王夫人夜於臥中夢見九色鹿，其毛九種色，其角白如雪，即託病不起。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王問夫人：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何故不起？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我昨夜夢見非常之鹿，其毛九種色，其角白如雪。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我思得其皮作坐褥，欲得其角作拂柄，王當為我覔之？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王若不得者，我便死矣。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王告夫人：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝可且起，我為一國之主，何所不得？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王即募於國中：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有能得九色鹿者，吾當與其分國而治，即賜金鉢盛滿銀粟，又賜銀鉢盛滿金粟。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，溺人聞王募重，心生惡念：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我說此鹿可得富貴，鹿是畜生，死活何在？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，溺人即便語募人言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我知九色鹿處。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」募人即將溺人至大王所，而白王言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此人知九色鹿處。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王聞此言，即大歡喜，便語溺人：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝若能得九色鹿者，我當與汝半國，此言不虛。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」溺人答王：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我能得之。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，溺人面上即生癩瘡。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "溺人白王：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此鹿雖是畜生，大有威神，王宜多出人眾，乃可得耳。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王即大出軍眾，往至恒水邊。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，烏在樹頭見王軍來，疑當殺鹿，即呼鹿曰：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「知識且起！",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王來取汝。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0452c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿故不覺，烏便下樹，踞其頭上，啄其耳言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「知識且起！",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王軍至矣。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿方驚起，便四向顧視，見王軍眾，已遶百匝無復走地，即趣王車前。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，王軍人即便挽弓欲射，鹿語王人：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且莫射我，自至王所，欲有所說。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王便勅諸臣：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「莫射此鹿，此是非常之鹿，或是天神。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿重語大王言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且莫殺我！",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我有大恩在於王國。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王語鹿言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝有何恩？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我前活王國中一人。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」鹿即長跪，重問王言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「誰道我在此耶？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王便指示車邊癩面人是。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "鹿聞王言，眼中淚出，不能自止，鹿言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人前日溺深水中，隨流來下，或出或沒，得着樹木，仰頭呼天：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『山神、樹神、諸天龍神，何不愍傷於我？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我於爾時不惜身命，自投水中負此人出，本要不相道，人無反復，不如負水中浮木。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王聞鹿言，甚大慙愧，責數其民語言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝受人重恩，云何反欲殺之？",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，大王即下令於國中：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「自今已往，若駈逐此鹿者，吾當誅其五族。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，眾鹿數千為群，皆來依附，飲食水草不侵禾稼，風雨時節五穀豐熟，人無疾病災害不生，其世太平運命化去。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時九色鹿者，我身是也；",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時烏者，今阿難是；",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時國王者，今悅頭檀是；",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時王夫人者，今先陀利是；",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時溺人者，今調達是。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "調達與我世世有怨，我雖有善意向之，而故欲害我；",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難有至意，得成無上道。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」菩薩行羼提波羅蜜，忍辱如是。",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說九色鹿經一卷",
        "from": "T03n0181a_001:0453a27_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]